        <mxCell id="a1cap" value="No per-agent identity   ·   No attribution   ·   No IAM-enforced boundary   ·   &apos;Safety&apos; lives on a sticky note" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontStyle=2;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="860" width="1320" height="24" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
